<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hans">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>佛说阿弥陀经 | 极乐世界经典</title>

<meta name="description" content="佛说阿弥陀经全文阅读 + 视频 + 简繁切换 + 护眼模式"/>
<link rel="canonical" href="https://www.amtb.cc/"/>

<style>
body{margin:0;font-family:serif;background:#121212;color:#e0e0e0;text-align:center;padding:20px}
h1{color:#ffd54f;font-size:3rem}
.box{max-width:900px;margin:auto;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);padding:20px;border-radius:16px}
#controls{position:fixed;top:20px;right:20px;display:flex;gap:8px;background:#222;padding:10px;border-radius:40px}
button{padding:6px 12px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid #555;background:transparent;color:white;cursor:pointer}
.light{background:#f5f5f5;color:#222}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div id="controls">
<button id="mode">亮</button>
<button id="zoomIn">A+</button>
<button id="zoomOut">A-</button>
</div>

<h1>佛说阿弥陀经</h1>

<div class="box" id="sutra">
<p>如是我闻。一时佛在舍卫国……极乐世界庄严清净。</p>
<p>舍利弗，从是西方，过十万亿佛土，有世界名曰极乐。</p>
<p>佛说此经已，欢喜信受。</p>
</div>

<script type="module">
let light=false;
let size=18;
const body=document.body;
const sutra=document.getElementById('sutra');

document.getElementById('mode').onclick=()=>{
light=!light;
body.classList.toggle('light');
};

document.getElementById('zoomIn').onclick=()=>{
size++;
sutra.style.fontSize=size+'px';
};

document.getElementById('zoomOut').onclick=()=>{
size--;
sutra.style.fontSize=size+'px';
};
</script>

</body>
</html>
